        <p>For comparison, play the example above from the <pubtitle>Moonlight Sonata</pubtitle> and try other pre<ndash/>dominant chords in its place, like <chord root="iv"/> (<chord root="F sharp" mode="m"/>)  or <chord root="ii" mode="diminished" bps="6"/>  (<chord root="D sharp" mode="diminished" bass="F sharp"/>), while noting the difference in effect.</p>
